unittitle_ssm: Paltsits Collection--Ulster County, New York
abstract_ssm: A collection of 114 items relating to the history of Ulster County, New York, in particular land transactions, legal papers and church records. All were collected by Dr. V.H. Paltsits.
corpname_ssm: Reformed Protestant Dutch Church of Kingston, New York
subject_ssm: Real property -- New York (State)  -- Ulster County.
title_ssm: The Historical and Statistical Gazetteer of New York State
The History of Ulster County, New York

The Early History of Kingston and Ulster County, N.Y.
History of Ulster County, New York: With Illustrations and Biographical Sketches of its Prominent Men and Pioneers
Collections of the Ulster Historical Society, Volume I
A History of Ulster County Under the Dominion of the Dutch
